name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.datanode.max.transfer.threads
description:
Specifies the maximum number of threads to use for transferring data
        in and out of the DN.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.containerlauncher.threadpool-initial-size
description:
The initial size of thread pool to launch containers in the
    app master.

name: dfs.client.deadnode.detection.probe.connection.timeout.ms
description: Connection timeout for probing dead node in milliseconds.

name: dfs.namenode.edekcacheloader.initial.delay.ms
description:
When KeyProvider is configured, the time delayed until the first
    attempt to warm up edek cache on NN start up / become active.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.max.connections
description:
Max allowed connections for the shuffle.  Set to 0 (zero)
               to indicate no limit on the number of connections.

name: dfs.client.failover.connection.retries
description:
Expert only. Indicates the number of retries a failover IPC client
    will make to establish a server connection.
